1
00:01:25,310 --> 00:01:29,880
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,530 --> 00:01:33,860
[Episode 9]

3
00:01:34,470 --> 00:01:37,430
The coroner has confirmed that Ms. Yang
had given birth before,

4
00:01:37,430 --> 00:01:39,630
but Madam Qin has never mentioned this.

5
00:01:39,720 --> 00:01:42,250
Do you know anything about this,
Third Madam?

6
00:01:42,750 --> 00:01:43,800
Your Highness,

7
00:01:44,110 --> 00:01:45,370
I know nothing of this.

8
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:48,520
When Concubine Yang entered the household,

9
00:01:48,520 --> 00:01:50,600
she was already over twenty years old.

10
00:01:50,600 --> 00:01:53,310
But my husband favored her greatly

11
00:01:53,310 --> 00:01:55,640
and gave her separate quarters to live in.

12
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:58,880
Although I am the principal wife,

13
00:01:59,520 --> 00:02:02,030
I never even received her tea offering.

14
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,960
I only heard that...

15
00:02:04,520 --> 00:02:07,030
she was exceedingly beautiful.

16
00:02:07,310 --> 00:02:08,509
As for anything else,

17
00:02:08,919 --> 00:02:09,960
I know nothing.

18
00:02:12,670 --> 00:02:13,830
In that case,

19
00:02:14,360 --> 00:02:17,020
we'll have to ask Master Qin An
to come in person.

20
00:02:21,540 --> 00:02:22,990
Your Highness, please allow me to report.

21
00:02:22,990 --> 00:02:23,870
My father

22
00:02:23,890 --> 00:02:25,050
is gravely ill

23
00:02:25,250 --> 00:02:27,380
and has been unconscious for two days.

24
00:02:29,200 --> 00:02:31,400
Since Master Qin An is so seriously ill,

25
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,900
I should pay him a visit in person.

26
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:44,490
Prefect Huo.

27
00:02:47,490 --> 00:02:48,850
Do you still need to investigate the well

28
00:02:48,850 --> 00:02:50,380
in the Purple Bamboo Grove?

29
00:02:50,390 --> 00:02:51,730
If you've finished investigating
that well,

30
00:02:51,730 --> 00:02:53,730
my grandma wishes to seal it
as soon as possible

31
00:02:53,730 --> 00:02:55,060
to ease people's minds.

32
00:02:55,250 --> 00:02:56,550
The search concluded last night.

33
00:02:56,550 --> 00:02:58,680
Madam Qin may handle it as she sees fit.

34
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,690
Thank you, Prefect Huo.

35
00:03:10,690 --> 00:03:11,450
Leave us.

36
00:03:35,390 --> 00:03:36,250
Your Highness.

37
00:03:42,170 --> 00:03:44,000
Has Master Qin An awakened?

38
00:03:44,420 --> 00:03:45,020
Not yet.

39
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,850
What did the doctor say?

40
00:03:49,250 --> 00:03:51,070
