for the past two days

41
00:03:51,070 --> 00:03:52,590
and hasn't even taken any medicine.

42
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:54,640
No doctor can do anything about it.

43
00:03:55,870 --> 00:03:56,930
If that's the case,

44
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,670
why not try my method?

45
00:04:00,150 --> 00:04:04,080
I think my treatment would be just right
for Master Qin An's condition.

46
00:04:08,390 --> 00:04:09,650
This should work.

47
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:11,590
Will this work?

48
00:04:12,010 --> 00:04:13,670
This is a secret method
from the Beiyi Tribe in Shuoxi,

49
00:04:13,670 --> 00:04:16,399
used specifically
for sudden unconsciousness.

50
00:04:17,640 --> 00:04:19,209
You just need to drive this iron nail

51
00:04:19,209 --> 00:04:21,810
through the brow into the brain
for seven days,

52
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:24,170
and it must not be moved during that time.

53
00:04:24,170 --> 00:04:25,170
After seven days,

54
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,430
once the blood clot in the skull
has been drained,

55
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:29,280
the patient will
naturally regain consciousness.

56
00:04:29,280 --> 00:04:29,890
Can...

57
00:04:30,470 --> 00:04:32,000
can he survive that?

58
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,800
Whether he survives,

59
00:04:34,850 --> 00:04:37,710
we'll know in seven days
after the nail is inserted.

60
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:48,350
He's awake, he's awake!

61
00:04:48,610 --> 00:04:49,200
See?

62
00:04:49,790 --> 00:04:52,450
I told you this treatment was just right
for him.

63
00:04:56,130 --> 00:04:58,190
Master Qin An, now that you're awake,

64
00:04:58,340 --> 00:05:00,940
